<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-font
      name="Poppins"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap"
    />
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#f2f2f2">
    <!-- Logo Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#FBF8F2" padding="10px 10px 0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          padding="0"
          src="https://www.stevenme.com/email-images/WOH1/WOHLogo.png"
          alt="Wags of Hope Logo"
          width="100px"
          href="https://wagsofhope.netlify.app/"
          align="center"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Hero Image -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          padding="0"
          src="https://www.stevenme.com/email-images/WOH1/WOFBanner.png"
          alt="Are you ready to make a difference"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Welcome Text -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="30px 20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          align="center"
          font-size="24px"
          font-weight="600"
          color="#333333"
        >
          Welcome to the Wags of Hope Family!
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          align="center"
          font-size="16px"
          color="#555555"
          padding="10px 20px"
          line-height="1.6"
        >
          At Wags of Hope, we believe that every dog deserves a second chance to
          love and be loved. We rescue dogs from uncertain futures, provide them
          with the care they need, and connect them with families who will
          cherish them forever. Your support helps turn heartbreaking stories
          into beautiful new beginnings — one wag at a time.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- DIvider -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding-top="0px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#f7c948" border-width="1px" width="70%" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Multi Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column
        padding="10px"
        inner-background-color="#FBF8F2"
        inner-border-radius="10px"
      >
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="20px"
          font-weight="600"
          color="#333333"
          padding-bottom="10px"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
        >
          🐾 Adopt
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="16px"
          color="#777777"
          line-height="1.5"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
        >
          Find your new best friend and change two lives forever&mdash; yours
          and theirs.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column
        padding="10px"
        inner-background-color="#FBF8F2"
        inner-border-radius="10px"
      >
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="20px"
          font-weight="600"
          color="#333333"
          padding-bottom="10px"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
        >
          🐾 Foster
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="16px"
          color="#777777"
          line-height="1.5"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
        >
          Open your home to a dog in need and help them transition to a forever
          home.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column
        padding="10px"
        inner-background-color="#FBF8F2"
        inner-border-radius="10px"
      >
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="20px"
          font-weight="600"
          color="#333333"
          padding-bottom="10px"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
        >
          🐾 Donate
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="16px"
          color="#777777"
          line-height="1.5"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
        >
          Every dollar provides food, shelter, and a second chance for a dog in
          need.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding-bottom="40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button
          background-color="#f7c948"
          border-radius="30px"
          padding="15px 30px"
          font-weight="bold"
          color="#333333"
          font-size="18px"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          href="https://wagsofhope.netlify.app"
        >
          Ways To Help
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- DIvider -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding-top="0px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#f7c948" border-width="1px" width="70%" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- About our Founder Text -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="30px 20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          align="center"
          font-size="24px"
          font-weight="600"
          color="#333333"
        >
          🐾 About Our Founder
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image
          width="150px"
          height="150px"
          src="https://www.stevenme.com/email-images/WOH1/WOHFounder.png"
          alt="Our Founder Caroline And Her Dog"
        />
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          align="center"
          font-size="16px"
          color="#555555"
          padding="10px 20px"
          line-height="1.6"
        >
          Wags of Hope started with one small act of kindness — and a heart that
          couldn’t walk away.<br /><br />
          Caroline founded Wags of Hope out of a simple belief: that every
          animal deserves love, safety, and a second chance.<br /><br />
          What began with helping one dog has grown into a mission fueled by
          compassion, community, and a whole lot of hope. Thank you for being
          part of this journey — it wouldn’t be possible without people like
          you.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- DIvider -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding-top="0px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#f7c948" border-width="1px" width="70%" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Txt before last CTA -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="0 20px 20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          align="center"
          font-size="16px"
          padding="10px 20px"
          line-height="1.5"
          color="#555555"
        >
          Every journey to a forever home starts<br />
          with hope &mdash; and with you.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Last CTA -->

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <mj-section
      background-color="#ffffff"
      padding-bottom="40px"
      padding-top="0"
    >
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button
          background-color="#f7c948"
          border-radius="30px"
          padding="0px 30px 15px"
          font-weight="bold"
          color="#333333"
          font-size="18px"
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          href="https://wagsofhope.netlify.app"
        >
          Be Part of The Journey
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <mj-section background-color="#f2f2f2" padding="20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="12px"
          color="#777777"
          align="center"
        >
          © 2025 Wags of Hope. All rights reserved.<br />
          1234 Hope Lane, Dogtown, USA
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#f2f2f2" padding="0 20px 20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Poppins, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="10px"
          color="#999999"
          align="center"
          line-height="1.5"
        >
          You are receiving this email because you joined Wags of Hope or
          expressed interest in supporting our mission.<br /><br />
          <a
            href="https://unsubscribe1.netlify.app"
            style="color: #999999; text-decoration: underline"
            >Unsubscribe</a
          >
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
